As a user(customer) 
I want to be able to navigate the site using the navigation menu
So that I can perform actions more quickly.



Scope

Navigation menu go to the web portal
The header of the site
Responsive design
It should work in Chrome, Mozilla, Safari browsers
It should work in Andriod, iOS


Precondition:

The online shop is launched 


Acceptance criteria:


Scenario 1:Registered user can successfully use the navigation menu
Given: User in on the main page 
When: User goes to another page 
Then: He can see the navigation menu on the header 


Scenario 2:Not registered user can successfully use the navigation menu
Given: User in on the main page 
When: User goes to another page 
Then: He can see the navigation menu on the header 









